data.description: Large, roomy townhouse with attached two-car garage and lots of storage space. Master bedroom and two additional bedrooms on the second floor; non-conforming fourth bedroom in the basement. South-facing, sunny unit with comfortable layout. New paint on main level; new water heater. Great location close to Anschutz Medical Center, Del Mar Park, the High Line Canal Trail, Aurora Hills Golf Course, Bicentennial Park, the Aurora Mall, shopping centers. Very low price for a home with 1860 square feet and a two-car garage!
